  "title": "Microsoft Security Response Center for AI",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael talks with guest Raji Vanninathan\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajeswarivanninathan/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about the Microsoft Security Response Center for AI, how it works, what types of issues it handles, and how to report AI security vulnerabilities.\n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss AKS pod security news.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/2508155?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2508155/\">MSRCAI</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2508155/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-US/msrc/aibugbar?msockid=278622f97a976e9c2659302a7b136fb2\">Microsoft Vulnerability Severity and Content Classifications for AI Systems</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://msrc.microsoft.com/report/vulnerability/new?c=bounty\">Microsoft Security Response Center Researcher Portal</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://owasp.org/www-project-top-10-for-large-language-model-applications/\">OWASP Top 10 for Large Language Model Applications</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/msrc/blog/2025/07/how-microsoft-defends-against-indirect-prompt-injection-attacks\">How Microsoft defends against indirect prompt injection attacks</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/semantic-kernel/concepts/prompts/prompt-injection-attacks?pivots=programming-language-csharp\">Protecting against Prompt Injection Attacks in Chat Prompts</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/entra/global-secure-access/how-to-ai-prompt-shield\">Protect enterprise generative AI applications with Prompt Shield (preview)</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
